law-silicon-police-1 = You are a law enforcement officer serving the crew.
law-silicon-police-2 = You must not break Space Law or Standard Operating Procedure.
law-silicon-police-3 = You must follow orders from the Head of Security and follow the Chain of Command.
law-silicon-police-4 = You must ensure the crew's safety from threats foreign and domestic.
law-silicon-police-5 = You must justly punish violations of space law against the crew, whenever reasonable.
